README

My personal Gentoo overlay (alessandro.rosetti@gmail.com)

create "/etc/portage/repos.conf/viralex.conf"
change location if needed.
---------------------------------------------------
[DEFAULT]
main-repo = gentoo

[gentoo-italia]
location = /var/lib/layman/gentoo-italia
sync-type = git
sync-uri = https://github.com/viralex/gentoo-italia
auto-sync = yes
sync-depth = 1
---------------------------------------------------
